      <p>
        <s>Workers in <name type="geo"><choice><orig>Bangladesch</orig><reg>Bangladesh</reg></choice></name></s>
      </p>
    </head>
    <body>
      <p>
        <s>We are <choice><orig>buing</orig><reg>buying</reg></choice> <choice><orig>to</orig><reg>too</reg></choice> much clothes but who made them and <choice><orig>whats</orig><reg>what's</reg></choice> the problems in the textile <choice><orig>industrie</orig><reg>industry</reg></choice>?</s>
        <s>A woman names <name type="person">Imke Müller-Hellmann</name> had many <choice><orig>question</orig><reg>questions</reg></choice> so she tried to answer them.</s>
        <s>In an interview with <ref target="a10gk2_2" type="author">Jörg Oberwittler</ref> she <choice><orig>discribes</orig><reg>describes</reg></choice> her <choice><orig>expierience</orig><reg>experience</reg></choice>.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>She was in <name type="geo"><choice><orig>Bangladesch</orig><reg>Bangladesh</reg></choice></name> in the city <name type="geo">Dhaka</name>.</s>
        <s>3000-4000 <choice><orig>textilefactories</orig><reg>textile factories</reg></choice> were around the city.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>The river was full with plastic and the trash collected on the bank.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>The workers working <choice><orig>allone</orig><reg>alone</reg></choice> and working <choice><orig>teen</orig><reg>ten</reg></choice> to <choice><orig>twelf</orig><reg>twelve</reg></choice> hours the day.</s>
        <s>They are proud of <choice><orig>themselfs</orig><reg>themselves</reg></choice> if they get 300 <choice><orig>boxershorts</orig><reg>boxers</reg></choice> in one hour.</s>
        <s>80 <choice><orig>procent</orig><reg>percent</reg></choice> of goods are textiles.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>There is a big issue of labour relations and it has to change.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>A solution could be that the politics change <choice><orig>somting</orig><reg>something</reg></choice>.</s>
        <s>We could buy more clothes from our land.</s>
        <s>Next time you go shopping think of the workers from <name type="geo"><choice><orig>Bangladesch</orig><reg>Bangladesh</reg></choice></name>.</s>
      </p>
